---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="skill-card stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="code" color="var(--accent2-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Full Stack</h2>
		<p>I am learning full stack programming. I am learning to work with different 
			programming languages and frameworks to improve my development skills both in 
			the front-end and in the back-end. I am passionate about technology and I am 
			willing to take on new challenges to improve my skills.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>DevOps/SysAdmin/SRE</h2>
		<p>I currently work as a Network Administrator at the University of Matanzas. My job is to ensure the operation and 
			security of the institution's network infrastructure. This involves the design, 
			configuration, maintenance, and monitoring of network devices such as routers, switches, 
			firewalls, and DNS servers.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="skill-card stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent2-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Teamwork</h2>
		<p>I believe in the importance of open and effective communication, cooperation and mutual 
			respect to achieve our goals effectively. I am always willing to listen to the 
			ideas and perspectives of others and collaborate in solving problems.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--glass-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.skill-card {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		transition: all var(--hover-transition);
	}

	.skill-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--glass-border);
		background: var(--accent-subtle-overlay);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 2rem;

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
